    "Besides that, there is some literature on the purpose [82,108,166] and practical challenges of AI ethics boards [68,134].",
    "There are also several case studies of existing boards, including Meta's Oversight Board [177] and Microsoft's AETHER Committee [115].",
    "And finally, there is some discussion of the role of AI ethics boards in academic research [24,163].",
    "Taken together, there seem to be at least two gaps in the literature.",
    "First, there is only limited work on the practical question of how to design an AI ethics board."
